title: 01/30 Fantasy Football Podcast: Offseason Intrigue (AFC/NFC East); Wentz vs. Foles
description:
Starting the show with some Teammate Combos! Eli & Beckham vs. Carr & Cooper (1:30), a Texans trio vs. a Falcons trio (8:45), Luck & Hilton vs Winston & Evans (10:30) ... Reacting to TEN's new Offensive Coordinator (18:00), and does Heath think Carson Wentz and Nick Foles are basically the same player (21:00)? Is Wentz a rising star? Is he a product of the system? ... The most intriguing player this offseason for NE (31:30), BUF (36:00), MIA (37:50), NYJ (41:12), DAL (45:15), NYG (48:50), PHI (52:28) and WAS (54:41) ... Your emails at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
